[I] Wayland animated wallpaper tool

[T] awww is an efficient animated wallpaper daemon for wayland, controlled at
[T] runtime.

[U] https://codeberg.org/LGFae/awww

[A] Leonardo Gibrowski Faé
[M] René Rebe <rene@exactco.de>

[C] extra/wayland
[F] CROSS

[L] GPL3
[V] 0.12.0

[D] ada63339ff954811d5717d55ae6714dc6d721bd585c35228cb2b8d67 awww-0.12.0.tar.gz !https://codeberg.org/LGFae/awww/archive/v0.12.0.tar.gz

cargoinstopt=
atstage native && hook_add postmake 5 "cp -vf target/release/{awww,awww-daemon} $root$bindir/"
atstage cross && hook_add postmake 5 "cp -vf target/${arch_target}/*/{awww,awww-daemon} $root$bindir/"
